 and they play sports.

11:54.320 --> 11:58.160
 I mean, this whole, you know, sort of movement

11:58.160 --> 12:01.840
 and going through mazes and playing tennis

12:01.840 --> 12:05.240
 and, you know, playing soccer and avoiding obstacles

12:05.240 --> 12:06.400
 and all of that,

