 Thank you for that wonderful journey

39:03.760 --> 39:04.880
 that you just took us on,

39:04.880 --> 39:10.480
 the darkest possible places of Greek song

39:10.480 --> 39:13.520
 to ending on this country song.

39:13.520 --> 39:15.120
 I haven't heard it before,

39:15.120 --> 39:16.800
 but that's exactly right.

39:16.800 --> 39:17.760
 I feel the same way,

39:17.760 --> 39:19.840
 depending on the day,

39:19.840 --> 39:22.240
 is this the luckiest human on earth.

39:22.240 --> 39:23.840
 And there's something to that,

39:23.840 --> 39:27.520
 but you're right, it needs to be,

39:27.520 --> 39:30.800
 we need to now return to the muck of life

39:30.800 --> 39:35.280
 in order to be able to truly enjoy it.

39:35.280 --> 39:35.760
 So it's...

39:35.760 --> 39:36.640
 What do you mean muck?

39:36.640 --> 39:37.200
 What's muck?

39:38.000 --> 39:39.280
 The messiness of life.

39:39.280 --> 39:39.760
 Yeah.

39:39.760 --> 39:41.440
 The things that were,

39:41.440 --> 39:44.480
 things don't turn out the way you expect it to.

39:44.480 --> 39:44.960
 Yeah.

39:44.960 --> 39:47.520
 So like, to feel like you're in the right place,

39:47.520 --> 39:48.800
 to feel lucky,

39:48.800 --> 39:51.680
 is like focusing on the beautiful consequences.

39:51.680 --> 39:52.080
 Yeah.

39:52.080 --> 39:55.440
 But then that feeling of things being different

39:55.440 --> 39:56.640
 than you expected,

39:56.640 --> 39:59.680
 that you stumble in all the kinds of ways,

39:59.680 --> 40:01.280
 that seems to be,

40:01.280 --> 40:03.200
 needs to be paired with the feeling of luck.

40:03.200 --> 40:04.640
 There's basically one way,

40:04.640 --> 40:06.400
 the only way not to make mistakes,

40:06.400 --> 40:07.760
 is to never do anything.

40:07.760 --> 40:08.000
 Right.

